CCU825 controller protocol library

Packages 
Package Description
ru.dz.ccu825
CCU825 protocol implementation, top level package.
ru.dz.ccu825.convert
Converters of ADC voltage to physical value for possible sensors on CCU825 inputs.
ru.dz.ccu825.data
Value objects representing specific types of values in CCU825 packets.
ru.dz.ccu825.payload
CCU825 response packet payload decoders.
ru.dz.ccu825.pkt
CCU825 request packets.
ru.dz.ccu825.push
Connectors to push data from CCU825 to other services.
ru.dz.ccu825.test
Tests main classes for the parts of the code.
ru.dz.ccu825.transport
Connectors to ModBus implementations.
ru.dz.ccu825.util
Exceptions, CRC, RC4.
ru.dz.nm8036
MasterKit 8038 board support.
test.ru.dz.ccu825
Unit tests for the CCU825 library.
test.ru.dz.nm8036
Unit tests for the nm8036 board library.
